# Tests that a graph can be created, four nodes and
# two pairs of cross edges and two other edges can be added, 
# and four nodes and six edges can be printed out.

# Create a graph
CreateGraph TheLordOfTheRing5

# Add four nodes
AddNode TheLordOfTheRing5 Frodo
AddNode TheLordOfTheRing5 Gandalf
AddNode TheLordOfTheRing5 Samwise
AddNode TheLordOfTheRing5 Arwin

# Add six edges
AddEdge TheLordOfTheRing5 Gandalf Frodo TheHobbit
AddEdge TheLordOfTheRing5 Samwise Frodo TheReturnOfTheKing
AddEdge TheLordOfTheRing5 Samwise Frodo TheTwoTowers
AddEdge TheLordOfTheRing5 Frodo Samwise TheTwoTowers
AddEdge TheLordOfTheRing5 Samwise Arwin TheFellowshipOfTheRing
AddEdge TheLordOfTheRing5 Arwin Gandalf TheFellowshipOfTheRing

# Print the nodes in the graph and the outgoing edges from Frodo, Gandalf, Arwin, Samwise
ListNodes TheLordOfTheRing5
ListChildren TheLordOfTheRing5 Frodo
ListChildren TheLordOfTheRing5 Gandalf
ListChildren TheLordOfTheRing5 Arwin
ListChildren TheLordOfTheRing5 Samwise